          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>At Wolf Ceramics, our vision is to cultivate a thriving community of passionate artisans who collaborate in a supportive and nurturing environment.</strong> We strive to honor the humanity of our team members, promoting balance and sustainable practices that enable us to craft beautiful, functional, and durable pottery for years to come.</p>",
