            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_be2be0c9-9023-4dff-bd10-b18d1ae23f6f.png",
            "title": "Embrace JOYL",
            "text": "<p><strong>Definition: ‘Joy in toil.’ </strong>The emotion of great delight or satisfaction caused by completing an exceptionally laborious task or project. It’s not every person who delights in making the same form again and again, striving for a little more deftness, a more perfect profile, or to finish a mug’s rim just right. </p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_qn3ajn": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_249c85d8-e74d-4b6f-8c0f-b9db5c0bfd9f.png",
            "title": "Collaborate Curiously",
            "text": "<p><strong>We approach our day-to-day with curiosity first. </strong>We are always learning from one another, asking questions, and working together to solve our ever-evolving array of production challenges. We believe that taking care of oneself is an act of caring for the entire team.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_bjRBgQ": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3_127326c2-a45c-4e1f-b34a-d99550838855.png",
            "title": "Create to Connect",
            "text": "<p><strong>Our ceramics are made to be used every day</strong>, to last through family dinners with little ones, and to enrich. meals spent with friends. Taking part in this work inspires us to gather, to celebrate the food that we eat and the people that we share it with.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
      },
