        "text_Apac94": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Wolf Ceramics, our vision is to cultivate a thriving community of passionate artisans who collaborate in a supportive and nurturing environment. </p><p>We strive to honor the humanity of our team members, promoting balance and sustainable practices that enable us to craft beautiful, functional, and durable pottery for years to come. Our signature aesthetic blends timeless design with a unique, joyful style that enhances the dining experience for our customers and hospitality partners. We aim to create handmade dinnerware that becomes a cherished part of everyday life, gracing tables and gatherings with the warmth and artistry of our dedicated craftsmanship. </p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
